---
import Base from "../../layouts/Base.astro";
const lastUpdated = "2026-06-27";
---
<Base
  title="MacroPilot — Privacy Policy"
  description="Privacy policy for the MacroPilot mobile app."
>
  <section class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-6 pt-16 pb-20">
    <p class="display-eyebrow mb-4">// MACROPILOT // PRIVACY</p>
    <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="mt-4 text-sm text-[color:var(--color-muted)]">Last updated: {lastUpdated}</p>

    <div class="prose-narrow mt-10 space-y-6 text-base leading-relaxed">
      <p>
        <strong>This is a placeholder.</strong> Final wording will reflect the app's actual data flows at launch. If you are reading this after the app is publicly available and the language still says "placeholder," email <a href="mailto:me@nate.cash">me@nate.cash</a> and Nate will fix it.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl mt-12">Who we are</h2>
      <p>
        MacroPilot is built by Nate Cash, sole operator, contactable at <a href="mailto:me@nate.cash">me@nate.cash</a>.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl mt-12">What we collect</h2>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
        <li><strong>Account info:</strong> email address (for sign-in and password reset).</li>
        <li><strong>Profile inputs:</strong> age, sex, height, weight, activity level, body-composition goal. Used to compute your macros.</li>
        <li><strong>Logged data:</strong> meals, foods, recipes, and weights you choose to log.</li>
        <li><strong>Device + diagnostic info:</strong> crash reports, basic device/OS version. Used to fix bugs.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-2xl mt-12">What we don't collect</h2>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
        <li>Location.</li>
        <li>Contacts, photos, or files outside what you explicitly attach to a log entry.</li>
        <li>Advertising identifiers. No ads. No ad networks.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-2xl mt-12">Third parties</h2>
      <p>
        We use a small set of vendors to run the service. The current list will be enumerated here at launch
        (hosting, error reporting, in-app purchase processor). We do not sell or rent your data, and we do not share it
        for advertising purposes.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl mt-12">Recipes</h2>
      <p>
        When you save a third-party recipe, MacroPilot stores its name, ingredient list, and a link back to the source.
        Cooking instructions stay with the original author.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl mt-12">Your rights</h2>
      <p>
        You can export or delete your account and associated data at any time from within the app, or by emailing <a href="mailto:me@nate.cash">me@nate.cash</a>. We honor verified deletion requests within 30 days.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl mt-12">Children</h2>
      <p>
        MacroPilot is intended for adults. We do not knowingly collect data from anyone under 13.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl mt-12">Changes</h2>
      <p>
        Material changes to this policy will be announced in-app and on this page. The "Last updated" date above always
        reflects the most recent change.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl mt-12">Contact</h2>
      <p>
        Questions, requests, or concerns: <a href="mailto:me@nate.cash">me@nate.cash</a>.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>
